+- one shared CKN-style localization regime;
+- one baseline burden, namely the full localized `I_flux[phi]` bundle;
+- one admissible gain notion in the same burden currency;
+- one typed debt-and-gain ledger with same-currency comparison and mandatory
+  transfer-lemma rules;
+- one anti-repackaging classifier;
+- and one nearest-prior-art audit format for later candidate packets.
+
+So the correct filing is:
+`scope lock passed, proceed to candidate slate and localized equation audit`.
+
+The next step should test concrete candidate packets on this frozen ledger
+rather than reopen endpoint, burden, or packaging menus.
